author: dreid
msg: - add a new template that takes a parameter! Been reading a book about xslt :-)
This means that we avoid a lot of essentially duplicated code by simply calling the
function that adds the section header, passing the title that should appear. I'd already
removed the links to the different sections and the anchors, so this is enough.
NB when passing the title you need to use the single quotes to stop the string being
treated as the name of an element to use.
